deadbeef: deadbeef (cross-platform audio player)
deadbeef:
deadbeef: DeaDBeeF (as in 0xDEADBEEF) is a modular cross-platform audio
deadbeef: player which runs on GNU/Linux distributions, macOS, Windows,
deadbeef: *BSD, OpenSolaris, and other UNIX-like systems.
deadbeef:
deadbeef: DeaDBeeF plays a variety of audio formats, converts between
deadbeef: them, lets you customize the UI in almost any way you want, and
deadbeef: use many additional plugins which can extend it even more.
deadbeef:
deadbeef: Homepage: https://deadbeef.sourceforge.io
